Module me.sbasalaev.tybyco

Package me.sbasalaev.tybyco.descriptors

package me.sbasalaev.tybyco.descriptors
Descriptors for Java classes, types and methods. All descriptors are immutable, may be shared and may be keys in the hashtable. Most of descriptor classes start with Jvm to avoid clashes with existing Java classes. Static imports from Jvm class may be used for brevity.
